<!-- BRIDGE Program -->
<section class="program-hero program-hero--bridge">
  <div class="program-hero__overlay"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <span class="program-hero__label font-mono">PROGRAM</span>
    <h1 class="program-hero__title font-display">BRIDGE</h1>
    <p class="program-hero__acronym font-mono">BREAKING RULES IN DECISIONS THAT GOVERN EDUCATION &middot; HIGH SCHOOL STUDENTS 14&ndash;18</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="program-quote">
  <div class="container">
    <blockquote class="program-quote__block">
      <p class="program-quote__text font-display">&ldquo;Students don't just attend school. They should help design it.&rdquo;</p>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="program-content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="program-content__grid">
      <div class="program-content__main">
        <div class="program-content__section">
          <h2 class="program-content__heading font-display">What It Is</h2>
          <p>BRIDGE turns high school students into education policy advocates. You find what's broken in your district&mdash;discipline policies, curriculum gaps, resource failures&mdash;build the evidence, and present reform demands to the people in charge.</p>
          <p>Not a simulation. You present directly to school board members and administrators. Your work produces policy briefs that enter the public record.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="program-content__section">
          <h2 class="program-content__heading font-display">The Problem</h2>
          <p>Education policy is made about students, not with them. School boards across DFW pass rules that shape young lives and almost never hear from the people those rules hit hardest.</p>
          <p>You sit in classrooms governed by decisions you had no hand in. BRIDGE ends that.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-content__aside">
        <div class="program-content__image">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523240795612-9a054b0db644?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=80"
