              <dt class="font-mono">Duration</dt>
              <dd>Full program cycle</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="program-details__item">
              <dt class="font-mono">Location</dt>
              <dd>DFW Metro Area</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="program-details__item">
              <dt class="font-mono">Deliverable</dt>
              <dd>Policy brief &amp; board presentation</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="program-phases">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="program-phases__title font-display">Six Phases</h2>
    <div class="program-phases__timeline">

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">01</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Find the Problem</h3>
          <p>Surface the education policy failures hitting your daily life&mdash;discipline, access, resources, representation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">02</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Build the Case</h3>
          <p>Gather data, conduct interviews, assemble the evidence that makes your argument undeniable.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">03</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Write the Brief</h3>
          <p>Draft a real policy brief with real recommendations for real decision-makers. Not a class project.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">04</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Learn to Hold a Room</h3>
          <p>Public speaking, persuasion, presence. Three minutes of testimony can change a vote.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">05</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Present to the Board</h3>
          <p>You walk in. You present your findings and reform demands. Directly to school board members. On the record.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">06</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Join the Network</h3>
          <p>Graduates join the BRIDGE alumni pipeline&mdash;young education policy advocates connected across DFW and growing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

